== 準備工作 ==
=== 危地馬拉 ===
因應熱帶低氣壓於5月29日早上形成，危地馬拉政府對[[沿海地區|沿海地區]]發佈熱帶氣旋警告。由於阿加莎在近岸形成，當局預料[[烈風|烈風]]程度的風力將於傍晚時分開始影響該地，令戶外準備工作難以進行。此外，阿加莎的移動速度緩慢，氣象部門預計會為當地帶來高達{{convert|30|in|mm}}的雨量，可能對危地馬拉、薩爾瓦多及墨西哥造成致命的[[洪災|洪災]]、[[山泥傾瀉|山泥傾瀉]]等。<ref>{{cite web|author=Stacey Stewart and Todd Kimberlain|publisher=[[國家颶風中心|National Hurricane Center]]|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-31|title=Tropical Depression One-E Special Public Advisory One|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep01/ep012010.public.001.shtml?|archive-date=2012-04-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EGeBiFO?url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep01/ep012010.public.001.shtml|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>

=== 薩爾瓦多 ===
因應暴雨可能持續影響[[薩爾瓦多|薩爾瓦多]]及[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]各地，當地官員疏散了約2000人<ref name="薩爾瓦多">{{cite web|author=Leslie Josephs|publisher=Reuters |date=2010-05-28|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Storm prompts El Salvador, Nicaragua evacuations |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN28218766._CH_.2420|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100604064812/http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN28218766._CH_.2420|archivedate=2010-06-04}}{{en}}</ref>。為應對本次災情，薩爾瓦多政府對境內發出了黃色預警，並按{{tsl|es|Sistema Nacional de Protección Civil de El Salvador|國家防災民防系統}}指示分配約52000名警員、緊急救援人員及軍人戒備<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=Eco Daiario|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Se intensifican lluvias de tormenta tropical Agatha en El Salvador|url=http://ecodiario.eleconomista.es/internacional/noticias/2186556/05/10/Se-intensifican-lluvias-de-tormenta-tropical-Agatha-en-El-Salvador.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601042509/http://ecodiario.eleconomista.es/internacional/noticias/2186556/05/10/Se-intensifican-lluvias-de-tormenta-tropical-Agatha-en-El-Salvador.html|archivedate=2010-06-01}}{{es}}</ref>。

== 影響 ==
=== 危地馬拉 ===
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Agatha_Guatemala_Flooding.jpg|thumb]]
[[危地馬拉|危地馬拉]]境內的火山[[帕卡亞火山|帕卡亞火山]]於風暴來襲2天前爆發，導致[[火山灰|火山灰]]迅速飄至[[瓜地馬拉市|瓜地馬拉市]]及[[拉奥罗拉国际机场|拉奥罗拉国际机场]]，並堵塞當地排水系統，加劇了風暴所帶來的破壞<ref name=Guatemala>{{cite web|url=https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Americas/2010/0601/Tropical-Storm-Agatha-floods-kill-150-cause-giant-sinkhole-in-Guatemala-City|title=Tropical Storm Agatha floods kill 150, cause giant sinkhole in Guatemala City|date=2010-06-01|accessdate=2020-09-15|author=Sara Miller Llana|archive-date=2020-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306180013/https://www.csmonitor.com/World/Americas/2010/0601/Tropical-Storm-Agatha-floods-kill-150-cause-giant-sinkhole-in-Guatemala-City|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>，拉奧羅拉國際機場一度需要關閉。

當地政府提醒，阿加莎所帶來的暴雨可能引發[[火山泥流|火山泥流]]，並加劇災情；不過，在[[咖啡|咖啡]]田工作的人認為，降雨能沖走[[咖啡樹|咖啡樹]]上的火山灰，對他們有幫助<ref>{{cite web|author=Robert Campbell|publisher=Reuters|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Guatemala girds for first Pacific storm of season|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE64S1A620100529|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601070939/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE64S1A620100529|archivedate=2010-06-01}}{{en}}</ref>。{{tsl|es|Instituto Nacional de Sismología, Vulcanología, Meteorología e Hidrología|危地馬拉國家地震、火山、氣象和水文研究所}}表示，當地在5月29日的總雨量達360毫米<ref>{{cite web|author=Lixion A. Avila and John Cangialosi|publisher=National Hurricane Center|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Tropical Storm Agatha Public Advisory Three-A|url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep01/ep012010.public_a.003.shtml?|archive-date=2012-04-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EGeeN0p?url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep01/ep012010.public_a.003.shtml|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。南部地區出現小規模的山泥傾瀉，阻塞了道路交通<ref name="ABC1">{{cite web|author=EFE|publisher=ABC Periódico Electrónico|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=La tormenta tropical "Agatha" tocará tierra guatemalteca el domingo|url=http://www.abc.es/agencias/noticia.asp?noticia=401252|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q5jav9CW?url=http://www.abc.es/agencias/noticia.asp?noticia=401252 |archivedate=2010-05-29}}{{es}}</ref>。

[[File:San_Miguel_Escobar_Tormenta_Agatha_2010_01.jpg|thumb]]出現泥石流]]
位於[[別哈城_(危地馬拉)|別哈城]]的[[水火山|水火山]]附近出現了[[泥石流|泥石流]]，導致9人死亡，13人失蹤，超過100戶受災<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Cuerpo de Bomberos Municipales de La Antigua Guatemala|date=2010-06-02|accessdate=2011-01-31|title=San Miguel Escobar arrasada por la tormenta Ágatha|url=http://bomberosdeantiguaguatemala.blogspot.com/2010/06/san-miguel-escobar-arrasada-por-la.html|archive-date=2011-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708025541/http://bomberosdeantiguaguatemala.blogspot.com/2010/06/san-miguel-escobar-arrasada-por-la.html|dead-url=no}}{{es}}</ref>；[[克薩爾特南戈省|克薩爾特南戈省]][[阿爾莫隆加_(克薩爾特南戈省)|阿爾莫隆加]]同樣出現泥石流，4人死亡<ref>{{cite news|last=Mines|first=Javier|title=Heavy rains brought by tropical storm Agatha kill 12 in Guatemala|url=http://wireupdate.com/wires/5819/heavy-rains-brought-by-tropical-storm-agatha-kill-12-in-guatemala/|accessdate=2010-05-30|newspaper=WireUpdate|date=2010-05-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601003835/http://wireupdate.com/wires/5819/heavy-rains-brought-by-tropical-storm-agatha-kill-12-in-guatemala/|archivedate=2010-06-01}}{{en}}</ref>。
 
因應災情惡化，多名主要官員在5月29日宣佈全國進入緊急狀態<ref>{{cite web|author=Herbert Hernandez|work=Reuters|publisher=MSNBC|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Pacific storm Agatha's rains kill four in Guatemala|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/37413356/ns/world_news-americas/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601053301/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/37413356/ns/world_news-americas|archivedate=2010-06-01}}{{en}}</ref>。國內多條河流水位急劇上升，幾乎氾濫。大量房屋受大規模洪水影響而損毀，多人要撤離至臨時避難所<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=El Correo|date=May 29, 2010 accessdate=May 29, 2010|title=Mueren cuatro miembros de una familia en Guatemala por la tormenta tropical 'Agatha'|url=http://www.elcorreo.com/vizcaya/rc/20100529/mundo/tormenta-tropical-agatha-guatemala-201005291951.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716084940/http://www.elcorreo.com/vizcaya/rc/20100529/mundo/tormenta-tropical-agatha-guatemala-201005291951.html|archivedate=2011-07-16}}{{es}}</ref>。

5月30日下午，當地傳媒報導，瓜地馬拉一共15人死亡，22人失蹤<ref>{{cite news|author=Juan Carlos Llorca|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Yahoo News|date=2010-05-30|accessdate=2010-05-30|title=Tropical Storm Agatha Kills 15 in Guatemala – First Tropical Storm of Season is Devastating|url=http://news.gather.com/viewArticle.action?articleId=281474978267566|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606180742/http://news.gather.com/viewArticle.action?articleId=281474978267566|archivedate=2010-06-06}}{{en}}</ref>。初部報告顯示，至少3500所房屋受損<ref name="CNN1"/>，超過11萬人需要撤離<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20100531/ap_on_re_la_am_ca/tropical_weather|title=Tropical Storm kills 99 in Central America|last=Staff writer|date=2010-05-30|publisher=Yahoo! News|accessdate=2010-05-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603065537/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20100531/ap_on_re_la_am_ca/tropical_weather |archivedate=2010-06-03}}{{en}}</ref>，逾2萬人無家可歸<ref name="HS1"/>。部分地區錄得超過910毫米雨量，是逾60年來最高的雨量紀錄，令阿加莎成為有史以來吹襲該國造成最高總雨量的熱帶氣旋，比1998年[[颶風米奇|颶風米奇]]更多<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/world/latin_america/10195619.stm|title=Death toll from storm Agatha rises in Central America|publisher=BBC News|date=2010-05-31|accessdate=2010-05-31|archive-date=2012-04-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EGh6908?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10195619|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref> 。翌日，死亡人數增至92人，另有95人受傷<ref name="CNN2">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/americas/05/31/honduras.storm.emergency/index.html?hpt=C2|title=Tropical storm kills 115 in Central America|last=Staff writer|date=2010-05-31|publisher=CNN News|accessdate=2010-06-01|archive-date=2010-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100604015751/http://www.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/americas/05/31/honduras.storm.emergency/index.html?hpt=C2|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。根據{{tsl|es|Coordinadora Nacional para la Reducción de Desastres|危地馬拉國家減災協調中心}}於災後發表的報告，超過34萬人受災，約10萬人流離失所<ref name=globalamericans>{{cite web|url=https://theglobalamericans.org/2017/05/climate-change-migration-guatemala-second-series/|title=Climate change and migration in Guatemala: Second in our series|date=2017-05-09|accessdate=2020-09-18|author=Nic Wirtz|publisher=Global Americans|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421111859/https://theglobalamericans.org/2017/05/climate-change-migration-guatemala-second-series/|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。

==== 出現沉洞 ====
{{main|2010年瓜地馬拉市沉洞}}
風暴來襲翌日，[[瓜地马拉市|瓜地马拉市]]出現了一個直徑約30米的[[沉洞|沉洞]]，有房屋、電話桿等倒塌<ref name="Guardian sinkhole">{{cite news|last=Walker|first=Peter|title=Tropical Storm Agatha blows a hole in Guatemala City|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2010/jun/01/storm-agatha-hole-guatemala|accessdate=2010-06-01|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2010-06-01|location=London|archive-date=2013-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130319204143/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/jun/01/storm-agatha-hole-guatemala|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.prensalibre.com/noticias/Vecinos-advertido_0_272372776.html|title=Vecinos habían advertidov|publisher=Prensa Libre|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603230639/http://prensalibre.com/noticias/Vecinos-advertido_0_272372776.html |date=2010-06-03|archive-date=2010-06-03|accessdate=2020-09-15|author1=A. RAMÍREZ|author2=C. BONILLO|author3=C. ORANTES}}{{es}}</ref>。這次的沉洞由[[污水渠|污水渠]]爆破引起，受阿加莎雨帶影響，災情進一步惡化，導致15人死亡，另有至少300戶居住在高危地帶，並未完全撤離。<ref name="National Geographic 2">{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2010/06/100601-sinkhole-in-guatemala-2010-world-science/#|title=Sinkhole in Guatemala: Giant Could Get Even Bigger|work=National Geographic|date=2010-06-01|agency=National Geographic|accessdate=2013-04-21|author=Than, Ker|archive-date=2013-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027182954/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2010/06/100601-sinkhole-in-guatemala-2010-world-science/|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref><ref name="Christian Science Monitor">{{cite news|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Americas/2010/0601/Guatemala-City-sinkhole-so-big-so-round-it-doesn-t-seem-real|title=Guatemala City sinkhole so big, so round it 'doesn't seem real'|work=Christian Science Monitor|date=2010-06-01|agency=Christian Science Monitor|accessdate=2013-04-21|last=Fieser|first=Ezra|location=Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic|archive-date=2013-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001030543/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Americas/2010/0601/Guatemala-City-sinkhole-so-big-so-round-it-doesn-t-seem-real|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>

==== 災後援與後續影響 ====
災後，多國向瓜地馬拉提供援助。當中[[巴西|巴西]]贈送了2萬噸[[玉米|玉米]]及5千噸[[飯|飯]]，而[[古巴|古巴]]亦派遣了一隊醫療隊協助救災。此外，[[歐盟|歐盟]]對瓜地馬拉提拱了240萬美元援助，[[世界銀行|世界銀行]]則考慮借出8500萬美元，作災後重建等<ref>{{cite web|url=https://latindispatch.com/2010/06/03/guatemalan-residents-return-home-after-tropical-storm-agatha/|title=Guatemalan Residents Return Home After Tropical Storm Agatha|date=2010-06-03|accessdate=2020-09-16|publisher=Latin America News Dispatch|author=Staff|archive-date=2016-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623042337/http://latindispatch.com/2010/06/03/guatemalan-residents-return-home-after-tropical-storm-agatha/|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>。經歷[[颶風斯坦|颶風斯坦]]及[[颶風米奇|颶風米奇]]後，瓜地馬拉遭受重大損失，加劇了國內社會混亂的狀況和經濟的不穩定性，並大幅增加了國內的孤兒人數，並導致{{tsl|en|Northern Triangle of Central America|中美洲三角}}（即瓜地馬拉、薩爾瓦多及宏都拉斯三國）出現一波兒童移居潮<ref name=globalamericans/>。2011年，共有4059名兒童為了移民至[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]及[[美國|美國]]，在中美洲三角地區邊境被拘捕，數字逐年上升，在2014年升至超過6萬9千人；同時，從該三國遷至墨西哥的人口在2009年至2014年間上升了7至13倍<ref name=globalamericans/>。

=== 墨西哥 ===
阿加莎為墨西哥南部帶來強風與暴雨，同時亦捲起了2至4米的大浪。在阿加莎的登陸地[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]東南部，有約120戶家庭需要撤離，而當局因應洪水的威脅，對該州發佈黃色預警<ref>{{cite web|author=EFE|publisher=Terra Noticias|date=2010-05-30|accessdate=2010-05-30|title=La tormenta tropical "Agatha" arrecia sobre el sur de México|url=http://noticias.terra.es/2010/espana/0530/actualidad/la-tormenta-tropical-agatha-arrecia-sobre-el-sur-de-mexico.aspx|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602025429/http://noticias.terra.es/2010/espana/0530/actualidad/la-tormenta-tropical-agatha-arrecia-sobre-el-sur-de-mexico.aspx|archivedate=2010-06-02}}{{es}}</ref>。
{{clear}}

=== 尼加拉瓜 ===
阿加莎在增強成為熱帶低氣壓前，曾為[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]帶來連場暴雨，一名女士被氾濫的河水沖走，其後不治<ref name="薩爾瓦多"/>。全國有多棟房屋受損。在[[埃斯特利省|埃斯特利省]]，有24人被困家中，需由{{tsl|en|Nicaraguan Air Force|尼加拉瓜空軍}}救出<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=Inside Costa Rica|date=2010-05-28|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Over 1,000 People Evacuated In Nicaragua Due To Heavy Rains|url=http://www.insidecostarica.com/dailynews/2010/may/28/centralamerica100052803.htm|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q5nPtVpx?url=http://www.insidecostarica.com/dailynews/2010/may/28/centralamerica100052803.htm|archivedate=2010-05-29}}{{en}}</ref>。

=== 薩爾瓦多 ===
受阿加莎的雨帶影響，全國均下起大雨，因此出現大面積洪水。在[[聖薩爾瓦多|聖薩爾瓦多]]等六個災情較嚴重的城市，官員呼籲當地居民盡快撤離至避難所。<ref>{{cite web|author=Mark Rohner, Sylvia Wier|work=Bloomberg Businessweek|date=2010-05-29|accessdate=2010-05-29|title=Tropical Storm Floods Homes; 5 Die in Guatemala, El Salvador|url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-05-29/tropical-storm-floods-homes-5-die-in-guatemala-el-salvador.html|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q6DIMKwz?url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-05-29/tropical-storm-floods-homes-5-die-in-guatemala-el-salvador.html|archivedate=2010-05-29}}{{en}}</ref>當地一共發生140宗山泥傾瀉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/world/latin_america/10195619.stm|title=Death toll from Agatha rises in Central America|last=Staff Writer|date=2010-05-30|publisher=BCC News|accessdate=2010-05-30|archive-date=2012-04-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EGh6908?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10195619|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並錄得超過400毫米雨量<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer |publisher=El Salvador.com|date=2010-05-30|accessdate=2010-05-30|title=Agatha tocó tierra, pero las lluvias siguen hoy |url=http://www.elsalvador.com/mwedh/nota/nota_completa.asp?idCat%3D6364%26idArt%3D4834035|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602194804/http://www.elsalvador.com/mwedh/nota/nota_completa.asp?idCat=6364&idArt=4834035|archive-date=2010-06-02}}{{es}}</ref>，導致6人喪生，2人失蹤<ref name="CNN1">{{cite news|author=Staff Writer|publisher=CNN|date=2010-05-30|accessdate=2010-05-30|title=Storm kills 18 in Central America|url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2010/05/30/storm-kills-6-in-el-salvador/|archive-date=2012-04-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67EGgIZAG?url=http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2010/05/30/storm-kills-6-in-el-salvador/|dead-url=yes}}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Mauricio Funes |agency=[[埃菲通讯社|EFE]]|date=2010-05-30|title=El Salvador declara alerta roja por "Agatha" que causó al menos 3 muertos |accessdate=2010-05-30|url=http://noticias.terra.es/2010/espana/0530/actualidad/el-salvador-declara-alerta-roja-por-agatha-que-causo-al-menos-3-muertos.asp|dead-url=yes}}{{dead link}}{{es}}</ref>。因應阿加莎為當地帶來廣泛破壞，總統[[毛里西奥·富内斯|毛里西奥·富内斯]]於5月30日宣佈全國進入緊急狀態<ref name="HS1">{{cite web|author=AAP|work=Herald Sun|location=[[澳大利亞|Australia]]|date=2010-05-30|accessdate=2010-05-30|title=Storm leaves 18 dead in Central America|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/storm-leaves-18-dead-in-central-america/story-e6frf7jx-1225873268969|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q7IbL2o2?url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/storm-leaves-18-dead-in-central-america/story-e6frf7jx-1225873268969|archivedate=2010-05-30}}{{en}}</ref>。

當地農業大受影響，共有{{convert|3162|acre|km2}}農地被水淹沒，損失超過6百萬美元。相反，當地的學校並沒有受到嚴重破壞，大部分在風暴過後仍能正常運作；在378所受影響的學校當中，有63所遭嚴重破壞。阿加莎在全國共造成3110萬美元損失<ref name="RedhumSitRep3">{{cite web|author=OCHA|publisher=Red de Información Humanitaria|date=2010-06-09|accessdate=2010-06-17|title=América Central – Tormenta Tropical Agatha Informe de Situación #3|url=http://redhum.org/archivos/pdf/ID_7838_BE_Redhum-Sitrep-No.Sitrep3_Tropical_Storm_Agatha-OCHAROLAC-20100608.pdf|format=PDF|archive-date=2010-08-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5rvAzIgc4?url=http://redhum.org/archivos/pdf/ID_7838_BE_Redhum-Sitrep-No.Sitrep3_Tropical_Storm_Agatha-OCHAROLAC-20100608.pdf|dead-url=no}}{{es}}</ref>。

=== 洪都拉斯 ===
阿加莎登陸後，殘餘雨帶逐漸影響洪都拉斯，並帶來洪水及山泥傾瀉等災害。持續的暴雨破壞了45棟房屋，1名男子因建築結構倒塌而死亡<ref>{{cite news|author=Staff Writer |agency=Associated Press|publisher=KOKH Fox 25|date=2010-05-30|accessdate=2010-05-30|title=Agatha leaves at least 16 dead in Guatemala, Honduras|url=http://www.wgme.com/template/inews_wire/wires.international/3bdf09b0-www.wgme.com.shtml|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20100530171554/http://www.wgme.com/template/inews_wire/wires.international/3bdf09b0-www.wgme.com.shtml|archivedate=2010-05-30}}{{en}}</ref>。因應災情嚴重，時任[[宏都拉斯總統|宏都拉斯總統]][[波尔菲里奥·洛沃|波尔菲里奥·洛沃]]宣佈全國進入緊急狀態，當地教育局下令南部部分城市學校停課<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=Cadena Ser|date=2010-05-31|accessdate=2010-05-31|title=La tormenta tropical Agatha deja 95 muertos a su paso por Centroamérica |url=http://www.cadenaser.com/internacional/articulo/tormenta-tropical-agatha-deja-95-muertos-paso-centroamerica/csrcsrpor/20100531csrcsrint_2/Tes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601212032/http://www.cadenaser.com/internacional/articulo/tormenta-tropical-agatha-deja-95-muertos-paso-centroamerica/csrcsrpor/20100531csrcsrint_2/Tes|archivedate=2010-06-01}}{{es}}</ref>。

